StringLiteralExpr.value: CMDS must be a 2-D cell array with 3 columns.
Specified graphics object handle is invalid or not supported.
Position must be finite numeric values
Mouse click option must be one of ''none'',''normal'',''extend'',''alternate'',''open'',''drag_on'',''drag_off'',''wheel'',''delay.''
Mouse position must be a 2-element vector.
Mouse wheel travel must be a scalar value.
Pause duration must be a positive scalar value.
Mouse button cannot be clicked during dragging.
DeltaT must be a strictly positive scalar.
DeltaT must be either a scalar or a vector with matching size to CMDS
